---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { withBase } from '../utils/path';
import { SITE_CONFIG } from '../utils/site';
---
<BaseLayout title="贡献指南 · Agent Pitfalls">
  <article class="prose-tight max-w-3xl">
    <header class="mb-8">
      <span class="eyebrow">CONTRIBUTING</span>
      <h1 class="mt-3 text-[32px] font-semibold leading-tight text-ink">贡献指南</h1>
      <p class="mt-3 text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-slate">
        Agent Pitfalls 完全开源，欢迎以任何形式贡献 — 提交新坑、补充修复方案、订正错别字、
        增加采集源、改进 UI、优化文档。
      </p>
    </header>

    <section>
      <div class="flex items-baseline gap-3">
        <span class="font-mono text-[12px] text-mist">01</span>
        <h2>提交新避坑条目</h2>
      </div>
      <ol class="mt-4 list-none space-y-2 p-0">
        <li class="flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-lavender-mist bg-paper p-3.5 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-slate">
          <span class="font-mono text-mist">[01]</span>
          <span>在 <code>web/src/content/pitfalls/</code> 新建一个 <code>.md</code> 文件，文件名用 <code>kebab-case</code></span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-lavender-mist bg-paper p-3.5 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-slate">
          <span class="font-mono text-mist">[02]</span>
          <span>按 <a href={withBase('/schema')}>SCHEMA.md</a> 填写 frontmatter（标题、严重程度、平台、症状、根因、修复、参考）</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-lavender-mist bg-paper p-3.5 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-slate">
          <span class="font-mono text-mist">[03]</span>
          <span>正文用 Markdown，<strong class="text-ink">至少 1 个可执行修复 + 1 个公开参考链接</strong></span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-lavender-mist bg-paper p-3.5 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-slate">
          <span class="font-mono text-mist">[04]</span>
          <span>提交 PR，CI 会自动校验 schema 和字段完整性</span>
        </li>
      </ol>
    </section>

    <section>
      <div class="flex items-baseline gap-3">
        <span class="font-mono text-[12px] text-mist">02</span>
        <h2>条目模板</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="code-block mt-4">
<pre class="m-0 border-0 p-0 font-mono text-[13px] leading-relaxed shadow-none" style="background: transparent;"><span class="tok-comment">---</span>
<span class="tok-key">title</span>: <span class="tok-string">简洁描述问题（一行）</span>
<span class="tok-key">summary</span>: <span class="tok-string">2-3 句话讲清楚发生了什么</span>
<span class="tok-key">severity</span>: <span class="tok-bool">critical | high | medium | low</span>
<span class="tok-key">platforms</span>: [<span class="tok-type">claude-code</span>, <span class="tok-type">generic</span>]
<span class="tok-key">categories</span>: [<span class="tok-type">tool-use</span>, <span class="tok-type">context-window</span>]
<span class="tok-key">symptoms</span>:
  - <span class="tok-string">用户/Agent 实际看到的现象</span>
<span class="tok-key">root_causes</span>:
  - <span class="tok-string">为什么会发生</span>
<span class="tok-key">fixes</span>:
  - <span class="tok-string">具体可执行的修复步骤</span>
<span class="tok-key">references</span>:
  - <span class="tok-key">title</span>: <span class="tok-string">来源标题</span>
    <span class="tok-key">url</span>: <span class="tok-string">https://...</span>
    <span class="tok-key">source</span>: <span class="tok-type">GitHub / HN / 知乎</span>
<span class="tok-key">contributor</span>: <span class="tok-string">your-github-handle</span>
<span class="tok-key">discovered_at</span>: <span class="tok-bool">2026-01-15</span>
<span class="tok-key">verified</span>: <span class="tok-bool">true</span>
<span class="tok-comment">---</span></pre>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section>
      <div class="flex items-baseline gap-3">
        <span class="font-mono text-[12px] text-mist">03</span>
        <h2>本地开发</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="code-block mt-4">
<pre class="m-0 border-0 p-0 font-mono text-[13px] leading-relaxed shadow-none" style="background: transparent;"><span class="tok-comment"># 安装依赖</span>
<span class="tok-prompt">$</span> <span class="tok-cmd">npm</span> install

<span class="tok-comment"># 启动开发服务器</span>
<span class="tok-prompt">$</span> <span class="tok-cmd">npm</span> run dev

<span class="tok-comment"># 构建静态站点</span>
<span class="tok-prompt">$</span> <span class="tok-cmd">npm</span> run build

<span class="tok-comment"># 运行采集器（可选）</span>
<span class="tok-prompt">$</span> <span class="tok-cmd">pip</span> install -r requirements.txt
<span class="tok-prompt">$</span> <span class="tok-cmd">python</span> -m collectors.run_all</pre>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section>
      <div class="flex items-baseline gap-3">
        <span class="font-mono text-[12px] text-mist">04</span>
        <h2>采集器开发</h2>
      </div>
      <p class="mt-4">
        新增数据源时，在 <code>collectors/sources/</code> 创建一个新文件，继承
        <code>BaseCollector</code>，实现 <code>collect()</code> 方法并返回标准化的
        <code>RawHit</code> 列表。详见 <code>collectors/README.md</code>。
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-12">
      <div class="card text-center">
        <span class="eyebrow">READY TO CONTRIBUTE</span>
        <h2 class="mt-3 text-[20px] font-semibold leading-snug text-ink">准备好贡献了吗？</h2>
        <p class="mx-auto mt-3 max-w-md text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-slate">
          哪怕只是订正一个错别字、补充一个参考链接，也是受欢迎的 PR。
        </p>
        <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-x-7 gap-y-3">
          <a href={SITE_CONFIG.github} rel="noopener" class="link-cta">GitHub 仓库</a>
          <a href={withBase('/schema')} class="link-cta">Schema 文档</a>
          <a href={withBase('/pitfalls')} class="link-cta">浏览避坑库</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>